                 As PG&E's site is very unreliable, this site might also be affected. Cloudflare caching is used to try to prevent this, but if PG&E's backend system fails, this site will as well.
              </p>
              <br>
              <p class="typograph-intro intro-copy">
                View a collection of my previous work projects below.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
